                <h1>Duke in the NBA: Irving, Cavaliers cling to top seed in the East with the postseason approaching</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/d3747a55-daf4-44dc-a7e6-0ecd0926cffa.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="&lt;p&gt;In&#x20;his&#x20;first&#x20;game&#x20;with&#x20;Brooklyn,&#x20;Irving&#x20;scored&#x20;50&#x20;points,&#x20;most&#x20;ever&#x20;in&#x20;a&#x20;Nets&#x20;season&#x20;opener,&#x20;and&#x20;did&#x20;not&#x20;turn&#x20;the&#x20;ball&#x20;over.&lt;&#x2F;p&gt;" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            <p>In his first game with Brooklyn, Irving scored 50 points, most ever in a Nets season opener, and did not turn the ball over.</p>

